<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
<head>
    <meta charset="utf-8">
    <meta http-equiv="content-type" content="text/html; charset=UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width,initial-scale=1.0,user-scalable=no">
    <title>图片</title>

    <!-- 自带 -->
    <link rel="stylesheet" type="text/css" href="views/lib/img.css">
</head>
<body>
    <div class="info">
        <p class="sourceType"><%= sourceType %></p>
        <p class="ipUrl"><%= ipUrl %></p>
        <% for(var i=0; i < list.length; i++) { %>
            <div class="ig"><img src="<%= ipUrl + list[i] %>"/></div>
        <% } %>
    </div>
    <div class="con">
        <!-- scrollamount 设置每次滚动时移动的长度（以像素为单位）默认值为 6 -->
        <marquee direction="up" scrollamount="3">
            沙扬娜拉-赠日本女郎 <br>
            ——徐志摩<br>
            最是那一低头的温柔，<br>
            象一朵水莲花<br>
            不胜凉风的娇羞，<br>
            道一声珍重，道一声珍重，<br>
            那一声珍重里有蜜甜的忧愁——<br>
            沙扬娜拉！
        </marquee>
    </div>
    <audio id="audio" src="views/images/半壶纱.mp3" autoplay loop></audio>

    <!-- jQuery -->
    <script src="http://apps.bdimg.com/libs/jquery/2.1.4/jquery.min.js"></script>
    <!-- 圣诞雪花 -->
    <script src="views/lib/snow/snow2.js"></script>
    <!-- 自带 -->
    <script src="views/lib/img.js"></script>
</body>
</html>
